	(text "CONNECTORS SHEET — populate following docs/03-schematic-spec.md SHEET 4\n\nBlocks:\n  4.1  Servos x5         : J4 (Base 35kg) J5 (Shoulder 35kg) J6 (Elbow 15kg) J7 (Wrist 15kg) J8 (Grip TBD)\n                           Pinout standard Miuzei: 1=GND_PWR, 2=+VSERVO, 3=PWM_x_5V\n  4.2  Expansion 2x6     : J15 - +3V3, +5V_LOGIC, GND, I2C SDA/SCL, SPI MOSI/MISO/SCLK/CS0, EXP_IO1/2\n  4.3  Mounting holes    : 4x M3 (Pad+drill 3.2mm) aux 4 coins (5,5) (95,5) (5,65) (95,65)\n\nDecoupling cap 100nF + 10uF placed within 5mm of each servo connector on the PCB."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
